title: The.Elder.Scrolls.V.Skyrim.Update.12-RELOADED
description:
The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Update 12 (v1.9.29.0) (c) Bethesda

        03/2013 :..... RELEASE.DATE .. PROTECTION .......: Steam
              - :.......... DISC(S) .. GAME.TYPE ........: RPG
                   
Note: this update works with any installed version of the game. A list of
what's new has been included.

--

The next chapter in the highly anticipated Elder Scrolls saga arrives from 
the makers of the 2006 and 2008 Games of the Year, Bethesda Game Studios.   
Skyrim reimagines and revolutionizes the open-world fantasy epic, bringing 
to life a complete virtual world open for you to explore any way you choose.

1. Unrar.
2. Install the update into the dir where the main game is installed.
3. Copy over the crack to that same dir.
4. Play the game.
5. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
